{"tid":1032413,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日俾大眾財務女員工玩，點算好","createTime":"2019-02-22T10:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T10:48:02.000Z","uid":155945,"like":32,"dislike":466,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"a032a7137c537c70e785a7a7dcd44a6b3153e868","tid":1032413,"uid":155945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T10:48:07.000Z","msg":"話說今日大眾財務打電話俾我，以下係對話<br />\n我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />       個大眾財務員工:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :你好呀，呢邊係大眾財務呀，請問你有冇攞現金嘅需要呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :有呀，借一個億得唔得㗎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  : 可以呀， 你有冇卡number？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 冇喎， 畀現金唔得咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :可以， 咁你住邊度呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我住太子呀(呢個時候 我個friend湊埋嚟 我就開埋喇叭一齊準備好好玩下佢)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 你住太子邊度呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :冇喔， 成個太子住曬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咁我點畀錢你呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 你嚟太子m記畀我咪得囉（ 我feel到我已經開始慢慢lean住個場）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 借一億你唔驚畀人偷咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 成個太子都住曬了， 唔驚啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :好， 咁我燒俾你囉(呢個時候我突然間覺得空氣安靜咗， 我同個friend四眼相望， 然後好唔爭氣咁笑咗幾聲默默咁cut咗佢線<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n直到現在我都諗唔到當時究竟點駁佢好， 各位巴打可唔可以幫幫手諗諗點駁佢"},{"pid":"95b38a603e905fae566bc9c857bd642061244bec","tid":1032413,"uid":155945,"like":7,"dislike":29,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T10:48:35.000Z","msg":"汽車推推"},{"pid":"392599109ae7833fc770e75a74ce8f42eba69393","tid":1032413,"uid":172169,"like":436,"dislike":9,"score":427,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T10:50:05.000Z","msg":"你玩人先，抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f742f2d70400aba418002e1f67fb7c10d19fabed","tid":1032413,"uid":158598,"like":251,"dislike":0,"score":251,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T10:50:41.000Z","msg":"條女幾幽默"},{"pid":"0ef18bd77247a6120154c90a0217c9ff6c0adf22","tid":1032413,"uid":155945,"like":30,"dislike":35,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"392599109ae7833fc770e75a74ce8f42eba69393","tid":1032413,"uid":172169,"like":436,"dislike":9,"score":427,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T10:50:05.000Z","msg":"你玩人先，抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T10:50:50.000Z","msg":"屌，呢d電話好騷擾囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51bd9da6c88a91642ca97a71734b0b487013534c","tid":1032413,"uid":237041,"like":196,"dislike":8,"score":188,"quote":{"pid":"0ef18bd77247a6120154c90a0217c9ff6c0adf22","tid":1032413,"uid":155945,"like":30,"dislike":35,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"392599109ae7833fc770e75a74ce8f42eba69393","tid":1032413,"uid":172169,"like":436,"dislike":9,"score":427,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T10:50:05.000Z","msg":"你玩人先，抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T10:50:50.000Z","msg":"屌，呢d電話好騷擾囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T10:51:50.000Z","msg":"一句唔洗 唔該就算啦 講咁多廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7c66f2f05fe50bf77354c70e1b65782c8ce91e","tid":1032413,"uid":29080,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T10:52:25.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"7eb5a